  bottom panel is physically NARROWER than the top despite sharing pixel width, since it's a
  smaller/denser panel centered in the body with room left over for the joysticks/D-pad/buttons).
  This is an illustration, not a photographic likeness - the actual live-preview ImageViews sit
  on top of the transparent-looking screen cutouts at these exact same coordinates (see
  activity_main.xml, where previewTop/previewBottom use matching margins and sizes).
-->
